according to Mr Ernest-Anotione Seilliere, chairman.
Mr Seilliere told shareholders at yesterday's annual general meeting that he
expected to see 'a significant boost to earnings' this year.
CGIP, which earlier this year raised FFr994m (Dollars 175m) from a
convertible bond issue, recently reported flat profits for 1993, at FFr547m
against FFr542m in 1992.
