write-off of goodwill, losses per share worked through at 7.63p (0.21p).
The directors said the restructuring had provided an opportunity to create
more added value through the provision of high quality products and
services.
However, despite the benefits now showing through, they said the group would
not show significant improvements on 1993 until the second half of the year.
